<subSubSection pageId="148" pageNumber="546" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="148.[1454,2661,292,565]" pageId="148" pageNumber="546">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1456,1803,372,405]" pageId="148" pageNumber="546">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Lesser Congo Shrew is rather rare throughoutits range, and may be threatened by habitat destruction, although it has been found in degraded areas.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
